Software dependencies
---------------------

Python:
* configobj
* networkx
* pydot
* suds (for Greek)
* numpy
* scipy
* scilearn kit
* h5py
* nose (only for testing)

Other:
* Graphviz (dot)
* TreeTagger for English, German

Most Python libs are included in the Enthought Python Distribution (EPD).
Note: "suds" is not and should be installed manually. Tested with EPD 7.2
64-bit for Mac OS X.


Data dependecies
----------------

* Dictionaries in Presemt XML format in directory $TG_BASE_DIR/_data/dicts
* Sorted lemma counts produced with Manatee in directory $TG_BASE_DIR/_data/counts
* METIX and PRESEMT evaluation data


Setup
-----

1. Set TG_BASE_DIR to the root of the Transglobal code

2. Run "source env/setup_env.sh" to setup shell environment

3. Run bin/setup_local_data.py to build local data



Unit testing
------------

1. Run test/setup.py to build cached data for unit testing

2. Run "nosetest test"




